  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd ; 3500 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba9 : 50 \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bakeries are at risk of being crippled; 3500 bakeries closed : 50% job loss",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Out of the 7,000 bakeries so far, more than 3,500 bakeries have closed due to fuel shortage in the country. About 50 percent of the 3 lakh workers lost their jobs.",
        "In this case, due to shortage of fuel, the bakeries are unable to continue their production activities and due to this, the bakeries will be paralyzed in the coming days, the All Sri Lankan Bakery Owners Association said.",
        "In this regard, Bakery Owners Association President N.K. Jayawardena commented,",
        "And there is a massive shortage of wheat. However, due to the current fuel crisis, the bakeries are unable to carry out any activities.",
        "In this regard, the bakery association requested the Prime Minister, the Ministry of Energy and the Ministry of Commerce to take action on the issues. But so far no solutions have been found.",
        "Bakeries have been declared an essential service by the government. Fuel for essential services was provided but not for the bakeries and bakery workers.",
        "Bakery owners and employees are facing various problems due to lack of fuel. Their behavior is affected.",
        "More than 3,500 out of 7,000 bakeries have been closed so far. About 50 percent of the 3 lakh workers lost their jobs.",
        "The employees working in the bakeries are unable to carry out the operations of the bakeries due to the lack of fuel to come to their services. They are waiting in line for days to get the fuel.",
        "Accordingly, the responsible party should investigate the matter and find appropriate solution. The bakeries have to close down completely for the next two days.",
        "Only vehicles are supplied with fuel. But there are no resolutions regarding bakeries.",
        "If this situation persists in the coming days, we will close the bakeries and fight on the streets. On behalf of the association, we are warning the government. He said that we will take to the streets and fight after next Monday."
      ],
